init

public void init()
Initialize the agent profile This method initializes initialize the agent. It first starts the agent entity thread and sets the state INIT.

kill

public void kill()
Kill the agent profile This method invokes the state and entity to kill the agent. The history is flushed to disk.

reset

public void reset(int round)
Reset the agent profile This method resets the internal state of the profile. it first resets the state of the agent by sending a RESET signal to associated behavior. It flushes the history and selects a new home for the vehicles.

Parameters:
round - the current round number

isAlive

public boolean isAlive()
Indicate whether agent is alive or not. This method returns true if the agent is still alive. One agent is alive only when the state and entity are both alive !

Returns:
\b true if the agent is alive, \b false otherwise
